</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="15.[151,1436,1298,1436]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">
Qualitative and metric characters (indicated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bertolani, R." box="[760,946,1336,1362]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="1 - 104" refId="ref11147" refString="Bertolani, R. (1982) Tardigradi (Tardigrada). Guide per il riconoscimento delle specie animali delle acque interne italiane. CNR, AQ / 1 / 168, 15, 1 - 104." type="journal article" year="1982">Bertolani, 1982</bibRefCitation>
, and by 
<bibRefCitation author="Bertolani, R. &amp; Marley, N. J. &amp; Nelson, D. R." box="[1047,1300,1336,1362]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="139 - 145" refId="ref11185" refString="Bertolani, R., Marley, N. J. &amp; Nelson, D. R. (1999) Re-description of the genus Thulinia (Eutardigrada: Hypsibiidae) and of Thulinia augusti (Murray, 1907) comb. n. Zoologischer Anzeiger, 238, 139 - 145." type="journal article" year="1999">
Bertolani 
<emphasis box="[1165,1217,1336,1361]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">et al</emphasis>
., 1999
</bibRefCitation>
) persuaded us to attribute our specimen to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Bertolani" authorityYear="1981" box="[510,692,1373,1398]" class="Eutardigrada" family="Hypsibiidae" genus="Thulinius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Parachela" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Tardigrada" rank="species" species="ruffoi">
<emphasis box="[510,692,1373,1398]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Thulinius ruffoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The species is a new record for 
<collectingCountry box="[1074,1139,1373,1399]" name="Israel" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Israel</collectingCountry>
but has been reported for many Italian localities, 
<collectingCountry box="[426,511,1410,1436]" name="Turkey" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Turkey</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry box="[572,654,1410,1436]" name="Russia" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Russia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
